CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN.DoIT_Address Street_Name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"

CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN.DoIT_Address Street_Name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"

 if not fValue : # if field value is <Null> (then it is False) return nothing

 if type(fValue) == int : # if value is an integer, make it a string and return it alone

 else: # if value is a string, add a space before it and then return it - unless it is the first field (street_number) then don't add a space
 if fName == "Street_Number":
 return fValue
 else :
 return " " + fValue

CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN_RalphLiu.DoIT_Address street_name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"

CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN_RalphLiu.DoIT_Address street_name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"

CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN_RalphLiu.DoIT_Address street_name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"

CalculateField cccGIS_Address.ADDRESSADMIN_RalphLiu.DoIT_Address street_name streetName(!ADDRESS!) PYTHON_9.3 "# get the street name from ADDRESS
def streetName(oldAddress):
 streetType = ['St', 'Pl', 'Dr', 'Way', 'Rd', 'Ln', 'Cir', 'Loop', 'Blvd', 'Pkwy', 'Ct', 'Ave']
 direction =['S', ' N', 'W', 'E']
 a = oldAddress.split()
 name = ''
 for i in range (1, len(a)):
 if (a[i] in streetType):
 break
 else:
 name += a[i] + ' '
 name = name[: len(name)-1]
 addressEle = name.split() # address element without street number
 if (addressEle[0] in direction): # the address has prefix direction
 return name[2: len(name)]
 else: # the address has no prefix direction
 return name[: len(name)]


"
